WEBVTT

00:20.770 --> 00:21.604
Hey.

00:22.105 --> 00:23.732
What are you still doing here?

00:24.691 --> 00:27.944
I'm sorry. I thought you were my friend.

00:28.028 --> 00:30.113
Let's go. Everyone's here.

00:32.949 --> 00:35.410
Wait. Why is he leaving?

00:37.537 --> 00:38.621
So it wasn't him?

00:39.622 --> 00:42.584
Mi-rae!

00:43.168 --> 00:44.461
Ms. Choi?

00:45.879 --> 00:47.672
Su-ji, a college friend.

00:47.756 --> 00:49.049
What?

00:49.883 --> 00:52.385
The campus is so big. I still get lost.

00:52.469 --> 00:55.138
I almost lost you on my way back
from the bathroom.

00:55.221 --> 00:56.056
Let's go!

00:56.723 --> 00:57.557
Go where?

00:57.640 --> 01:00.185
What? We said we would go together.

01:01.394 --> 01:02.479
Over there.

01:05.315 --> 01:08.151
Yay, we're here!

01:08.234 --> 01:09.527
Isn't it great?

01:09.611 --> 01:10.779
"Freshmen"?

01:10.862 --> 01:12.030
WELCOME, FRESHMEN!

01:12.113 --> 01:15.158
I'm not a freshman, am I?

01:15.241 --> 01:16.409
No way.

01:16.493 --> 01:17.494
How much is this?

01:17.577 --> 01:18.536
STUDENT COUNCIL

01:18.620 --> 01:21.206
It's so pretty. Can I have this?

01:21.706 --> 01:22.540
Thank you!

01:23.875 --> 01:25.085
-You there!
-I got this.

01:25.168 --> 01:26.169
Freshmen!

01:49.651 --> 01:51.319
You gotta be shitting me.

01:57.784 --> 01:59.744
Let's go. That's awful.

01:59.828 --> 02:01.454
Join us in the near future.

02:01.538 --> 02:02.413
Never.

02:02.497 --> 02:03.623
Not you!

02:03.706 --> 02:04.707
Go away!

02:05.750 --> 02:06.626
Take a look.

02:06.709 --> 02:08.002
Check it out. It's fun.

02:08.086 --> 02:09.546
Come check us out.

02:09.629 --> 02:11.339
-This way!
-Come this way.

02:11.422 --> 02:15.009
-Take a quick look.
-Check out what we're all about.

02:16.719 --> 02:18.429
-We have cameras.
-Show us your kicks!

02:18.513 --> 02:20.640
-We're offering free photos!
-Free pictures!

02:20.723 --> 02:23.143
Why is this line so long, Ms. Choi?

02:23.226 --> 02:24.227
Hey!

02:24.310 --> 02:27.188
Don't call me that.
You're weirding me out.

02:29.399 --> 02:32.277
I know, right? Girl, that was so weird!

02:33.653 --> 02:37.323
They must be lining up to get tickets
for the kumdo match today.

02:37.407 --> 02:40.368
I heard in the bathroom earlier
that it was sold out.

02:40.451 --> 02:42.745
Are they waiting
to get canceled tickets or what?

02:42.829 --> 02:45.165
The kumdo club must be really popular.

02:46.332 --> 02:49.836
I heard it's even more popular
than the soccer and hockey teams here.

02:51.671 --> 02:53.798
No way! You got tickets?

02:53.882 --> 02:56.134
Where did you get these? That's insane!

02:56.217 --> 02:58.094
I'm supposed to go here, aren't I?

02:59.012 --> 03:00.388
You have to go.

03:01.431 --> 03:02.432
Come along now.

03:02.515 --> 03:03.850
It's this way.

03:22.535 --> 03:23.620
He's here!

03:23.703 --> 03:25.330
13TH KUMDO FRIENDLY
HANSAE VS KOSAN

03:26.706 --> 03:27.957
What's going on?

03:28.625 --> 03:30.543
Didn't I tell you not to stand here?

03:30.627 --> 03:31.878
Why not?

03:31.961 --> 03:33.630
You're blocking the view!

03:33.713 --> 03:35.632
-Damn it!
-What did you say?

03:36.257 --> 03:39.219
Who are they?
Part of a fan club or something?

03:39.302 --> 03:40.136
I guess so.

03:40.220 --> 03:43.348
The Hansae-Kosan kumdo friendly match
will begin soon.

03:43.431 --> 03:46.559
Hansae University!

03:46.643 --> 03:47.936
EUN-HO, WE LOVE YOU

03:48.019 --> 03:51.606
Hansae University!

03:51.689 --> 03:54.943
-Hansae University!
-Kosan University!

03:55.026 --> 03:55.860
Begin!

03:59.364 --> 04:01.241
Head strike!

04:20.426 --> 04:24.514
-Seo Eun-ho of Hansae University has won.
-Eun-ho!

04:24.597 --> 04:28.559
In the next match,
Park Myeong-seong of Hansae University

04:28.643 --> 04:31.813
will be facing
An Hong-mo of Kosan University.

04:31.896 --> 04:33.564
Please remain seated.

04:48.454 --> 04:50.415
So cool!

04:50.498 --> 04:52.333
He's amazing.

05:06.139 --> 05:10.018
Congratulations, Ms. Seo Mi-rae,
on meeting your second date!

05:20.403 --> 05:21.446
I knew it.

05:22.238 --> 05:23.448
It was you.

05:30.038 --> 05:33.833
EPISODE 3
FIRST LOVE 101

05:37.003 --> 05:38.004
HANSAE KUMDO CLUB

05:38.087 --> 05:40.423
Are you guys joining because of Eun-ho?

05:40.506 --> 05:41.341
No.

05:42.592 --> 05:45.178
It's okay. That's why we joined too.

05:45.678 --> 05:48.598
-You want to get to know him better, huh?
-Yes!

05:49.557 --> 05:51.642
Then you'll have to get past us first.

05:56.939 --> 05:59.317
Is Seo Eun-ho really that popular?

06:00.109 --> 06:01.736
How could he not be?

06:01.819 --> 06:04.364
I'll bet all the girls here
wish he'd go on

06:04.447 --> 06:08.201
to earn his master's and doctorate
and become a professor here.

06:08.701 --> 06:11.162
Good thing the architecture program
is five years long.

06:11.245 --> 06:12.288
He's not a PE major?

06:12.372 --> 06:15.375
Wow, he's in architecture.
He must be smart too.

06:15.958 --> 06:19.629
Eun-ho's good enough to run a country,
not just a company!

06:19.712 --> 06:21.172
Totally!

06:21.756 --> 06:24.926
So the most popular guy on campus
likes me?

06:26.719 --> 06:27.929
That's a decent plot.

06:28.012 --> 06:30.014
-Why are you laughing?
-What?

06:32.683 --> 06:34.060
It's nothing.

06:37.730 --> 06:38.940
Introduce myself?

06:42.777 --> 06:46.072
I'm Seo Mi-rae, a freshman.
Looking forward to it.

06:55.623 --> 06:56.874
Where am I now?

06:58.751 --> 07:00.044
He's so handsome.

07:00.128 --> 07:03.214
All right, freshmen.
It's our first time seeing each other.

07:03.714 --> 07:04.549
Say hello.

07:04.632 --> 07:08.177
-Hello.
-Hello.

07:11.514 --> 07:12.598
Hey.

07:12.682 --> 07:14.058
What are you still doing here?

07:16.144 --> 07:18.312
It's the girl I saw earlier.

07:18.396 --> 07:21.149
Hey, isn't the club president
just gorgeous?

07:22.984 --> 07:23.985
She is.

07:41.586 --> 07:45.214
Kumdo is the best sport
for training one's body and mind.

07:45.298 --> 07:50.178
We will help you enjoy every aspect of it,
from the basic stances to sparring.

07:50.678 --> 07:54.348
Since it's your first day,
let's start with the basic footwork.

07:55.349 --> 07:56.559
Any volunteers?

07:57.268 --> 07:58.686
Who wants to give it a go?

08:07.487 --> 08:09.405
Good. Come on out, then.

08:09.989 --> 08:10.823
Sorry?

08:13.618 --> 08:14.744
No, I'm good.

08:14.827 --> 08:16.204
Come out. It's okay.

08:16.287 --> 08:17.163
Get out there.

08:22.043 --> 08:23.377
What was your name again?

08:23.461 --> 08:25.880
It's Seo Mi-rae.

08:32.386 --> 08:35.806
It would be nice
if someone could help out.

08:38.351 --> 08:40.186
All right. Help us, will you?

08:40.269 --> 08:42.939
They probably all came to see you anyway.

08:44.774 --> 08:45.608
Shall I?

08:48.986 --> 08:50.196
Is that okay with you?

08:51.989 --> 08:52.823
Yes.

08:59.872 --> 09:00.706
Hi.

09:02.166 --> 09:03.668
Hello.

09:03.751 --> 09:05.294
Have you tried kumdo before?

09:06.671 --> 09:07.838
No, I haven't.

09:13.261 --> 09:14.095
Here.

09:16.931 --> 09:18.266
Hold it like this.

09:19.392 --> 09:20.935
Right foot, forward.

09:24.021 --> 09:25.481
How is it? Comfortable?

09:26.732 --> 09:27.567
Yes.

09:29.318 --> 09:30.403
High stance.

09:32.238 --> 09:33.239
Head strike.

09:33.322 --> 09:35.032
And this is the middle stance,

09:35.658 --> 09:37.743
which will be your basic stance.

09:37.827 --> 09:38.869
Want to give it a go?

09:40.204 --> 09:41.038
Yes.

09:47.253 --> 09:48.087
Go ahead.

09:50.506 --> 09:51.340
Head strike.

09:59.932 --> 10:01.225
What was that?

10:02.226 --> 10:03.811
Is this really your first time?

10:03.894 --> 10:06.063
This is my first time.

10:07.440 --> 10:11.527
What just happened?
I usually have two left feet.

10:13.738 --> 10:17.033
You're really athletic, huh?
Let's try that again.

10:18.951 --> 10:19.785
Okay.

10:59.075 --> 11:02.495
Wasn't she a blur just now?
What did I just see?

11:02.995 --> 11:04.288
No way.

11:04.789 --> 11:06.666
Mi-rae, you've really got talent.

11:07.416 --> 11:09.835
Come on.
Eun-ho was obviously going easy on her.

11:09.919 --> 11:10.878
I wasn't.

11:12.129 --> 11:13.506
Great job.

11:14.882 --> 11:16.258
I'll be looking forward to it.

11:18.678 --> 11:19.512
Okay.

11:21.138 --> 11:23.182
-Head strike!
-Head strike.

11:23.265 --> 11:25.351
-He's just so cool.
-One.

11:25.851 --> 11:27.186
-I know!
-Head strike.

11:27.269 --> 11:29.188
-Look how stable he is.
-Middle stance.

11:29.271 --> 11:31.774
He's just so insanely buff!

11:31.857 --> 11:33.025
You know it!

11:33.818 --> 11:35.361
Like you're walking. Watch me.

11:35.444 --> 11:36.320
One!

11:36.404 --> 11:37.363
Head strike!

11:38.239 --> 11:39.407
Very good.

11:41.033 --> 11:42.410
Mr. Ko?

11:51.544 --> 11:54.422
Why are you guys just standing here?
Is something wrong?

11:55.715 --> 11:57.341
Jung-pil, kumdo club senior.

11:58.008 --> 11:59.009
Actually…

11:59.885 --> 12:00.720
What's your name?

12:02.179 --> 12:03.347
-It's Su-ji.
-Su-ji?

12:03.431 --> 12:04.849
-Yes.
-Su-ji, come over here.

12:04.932 --> 12:05.808
Okay.

12:06.350 --> 12:09.562
-The key to kumdo is smooth movement.
-Okay.

12:09.645 --> 12:10.771
Head strike!

12:11.522 --> 12:12.440
Head strike!

12:12.523 --> 12:14.233
That was so smooth.

12:14.316 --> 12:15.317
You try.

12:17.361 --> 12:18.529
Head strike!

12:19.029 --> 12:20.906
Hey, keep an eye on everyone.

12:20.990 --> 12:22.158
Sure.

12:22.241 --> 12:23.492
Head strike!

12:27.747 --> 12:28.581
Eun-ho.

12:31.584 --> 12:34.378
-Where are you off to?
-The library. Why do you ask?

12:35.838 --> 12:37.923
Would you like to have lunch with me?

12:39.091 --> 12:40.050
All together?

12:41.761 --> 12:42.595
No.

12:43.679 --> 12:44.930
Just the two of us?

12:45.598 --> 12:46.432
Yes.

12:49.810 --> 12:51.312
You're quite impatient, huh?

12:53.063 --> 12:55.316
Next time, once we know each other better.

12:56.192 --> 12:57.610
-What?
-Take care.

12:59.236 --> 13:00.863
Eun-ho?

13:00.946 --> 13:02.031
Hey, Eun-ho!

13:03.532 --> 13:05.201
Where are you going? Let me come.

13:05.284 --> 13:06.202
Let's go eat.

13:11.415 --> 13:13.417
Weren't you supposed to have
fallen for me?

13:13.501 --> 13:14.877
Why should he?

13:14.960 --> 13:18.005
He should be into me.
This is Boyfriend on Demand, after all.

13:18.506 --> 13:21.425
I think you may have gotten
the wrong idea.

13:21.509 --> 13:22.343
Wrong idea?

13:23.302 --> 13:27.807
Did you think that all 900 guys here
would be chasing after you from the start?

13:29.600 --> 13:31.268
But…

13:35.147 --> 13:36.649
Choi Si-woo liked me from the--

13:36.732 --> 13:40.069
That's just how that scenario was written.

13:43.155 --> 13:43.989
SPRING, AND YOU

13:44.073 --> 13:46.992
You don't look it, but you've got
a pretty bad princess complex.

13:47.827 --> 13:51.539
Are you saying Seo Eun-ho
might not ever end up falling for me?

13:51.622 --> 13:55.543
There's no telling that.
Some dates are more difficult than others.

13:56.252 --> 13:59.839
If I have to work for it,
how's it any different from reality?

13:59.922 --> 14:03.259
Would you rather date another guy?
Shall we move on?

14:07.680 --> 14:09.265
No, wait. Hey!

14:09.348 --> 14:10.349
Hold on a second.

14:10.432 --> 14:13.769
If you're not feeling it, just move on.
You don't have much time.

14:13.853 --> 14:15.771
I know. My time…

14:16.772 --> 14:17.606
Time?

14:29.994 --> 14:30.828
Jesus.

14:44.049 --> 14:45.259
Kyeong-nam.

14:46.635 --> 14:47.636
Man, look at her.

14:51.390 --> 14:52.308
You want coffee?

14:52.391 --> 14:55.185
PlanC had a decent first episode as well.

15:00.524 --> 15:01.984
But Yun Song's tough, right?

15:03.235 --> 15:04.737
I knew what we were up against.

15:05.321 --> 15:07.990
Did you really ask to be moved to Fridays?

15:08.073 --> 15:08.908
No.

15:10.534 --> 15:11.994
Ms. Seo didn't seem to think so.

15:12.578 --> 15:14.830
Obviously. She doesn't like me, after all.

15:16.415 --> 15:17.291
Don't you?

15:27.509 --> 15:28.344
What?

15:29.887 --> 15:30.846
Yes?

15:32.556 --> 15:33.390
Come in.

15:37.770 --> 15:39.229
Did you want to see me?

15:40.981 --> 15:42.900
I just got off a call with Yun Song.

15:43.400 --> 15:44.860
What? What was it about?

15:44.944 --> 15:47.446
What else would that woman call me for?

15:49.615 --> 15:51.742
Honestly, I want to end this series.

15:51.825 --> 15:53.369
I'm so sick and tired of it!

15:53.452 --> 15:55.871
Please save me.

15:59.875 --> 16:03.003
You don't mean
she's thinking about quitting?

16:03.087 --> 16:04.630
-She said she's quitting?
-What?

16:04.713 --> 16:06.423
-What?
-No.

16:06.507 --> 16:07.466
Damn it.

16:08.217 --> 16:09.259
Then why did she…

16:10.469 --> 16:13.889
She wants two weeks off.
Otherwise, we'll be attending her funeral.

16:14.765 --> 16:17.226
Ms. Yun has been through a lot recently.

16:18.769 --> 16:19.603
Great work.

16:20.938 --> 16:23.565
-Sorry?
-I liked it. Keep it up.

16:24.358 --> 16:27.069
-I don't get why you were whining so much.
-Please…

16:27.152 --> 16:30.322
While Yun is on her break,
think about the next episodes.

16:31.991 --> 16:34.034
You approved her break?

16:35.828 --> 16:37.496
Seo Mi-rae is free on a weekday?

16:37.579 --> 16:39.415
It smells so good. Hurry up.

16:41.250 --> 16:45.254
So you'll be free for two weeks.
Should we go to Jeju over the weekend?

16:45.337 --> 16:47.464
Jeju? Don't even think about it.

16:47.548 --> 16:49.883
I have other authors to take care of.

16:51.176 --> 16:55.139
I've always thought that being a producer
is not worth the grind.

16:55.222 --> 16:56.390
Not worth it at all!

16:57.349 --> 16:59.268
It looks so good!

17:01.645 --> 17:02.479
Hey, Ji-yeon.

17:02.980 --> 17:08.318
Say you could go back to being 20.
What would you want to try?

17:12.948 --> 17:13.782
Sex.

17:16.326 --> 17:17.536
Not that kind of stuff!

17:19.580 --> 17:22.708
What's this out of the blue?
What would you do if you went back?

17:24.376 --> 17:27.880
I'd want my life to be
completely different from this one.

17:27.963 --> 17:29.048
The exact opposite.

17:29.131 --> 17:31.091
-The opposite?
-Yeah.

17:31.175 --> 17:34.928
You know, if I fell for someone,
I'd just go straight for him.

17:35.012 --> 17:36.388
Come what may,

17:37.014 --> 17:41.101
I'd be way more proactive
about pretty much everything.

17:43.729 --> 17:46.690
Hey, you're cracking me up!

17:46.774 --> 17:47.733
What's so funny?

17:47.816 --> 17:51.028
You were super proactive when you were 20.

17:51.111 --> 17:51.987
I was?

17:52.071 --> 17:53.155
Yes!

17:54.656 --> 17:56.825
Se-june had a crush on You-mi,

17:56.909 --> 18:00.245
and you kept trying to win him over
until you made him yours.

18:01.914 --> 18:03.916
You forgot, didn't you?

18:05.292 --> 18:08.378
You-mi sure was popular back in the day.

18:09.129 --> 18:11.340
Not as popular as me, but still.

18:13.509 --> 18:16.303
You're right. I was like that.

18:19.807 --> 18:21.391
So how did I end up like this?

18:22.434 --> 18:25.604
I guess dating him for too long
changed you.

18:26.188 --> 18:27.272
And you got older.

18:27.856 --> 18:29.233
I feel like

18:30.025 --> 18:32.611
we had a really good thing going
in the beginning.

18:34.446 --> 18:36.198
Yeah, you really did.

18:36.740 --> 18:38.450
I envied you guys back then.

18:47.209 --> 18:49.086
Seo Eun-ho, I must say,

18:49.670 --> 18:51.463
is not an easy one.

18:53.173 --> 18:56.677
You were super proactive when you were 20.

18:59.596 --> 19:01.098
Should I just go for it?

19:01.598 --> 19:03.934
Temples in classical architecture

19:04.017 --> 19:08.272
can be classified by the number of columns
in the front and rear facades.

19:09.064 --> 19:11.567
It's called "distyle"
when there are two columns,

19:11.650 --> 19:13.902
"tetrastyle" when there are four,

19:13.986 --> 19:16.780
and "hexastyle" when there are six.

19:17.281 --> 19:18.907
When it comes to the hexastyle…

19:31.837 --> 19:32.921
Hello.

19:33.422 --> 19:34.256
Hi.

19:34.840 --> 19:35.799
Can I sit here?

19:35.883 --> 19:37.259
Be my guest.

19:41.930 --> 19:42.764
Can you move over?

19:43.682 --> 19:44.766
Just a sec.

19:54.276 --> 19:55.569
Go ahead.

19:59.448 --> 20:01.366
So you're going to keep that up, huh?

20:03.202 --> 20:06.538
The columns of a temple can be classified
according to their forms…

20:06.622 --> 20:12.127
Since I decided to go for it,
I'm going to pull out all of my old moves.

20:15.756 --> 20:17.049
Where are we right now?

20:26.183 --> 20:27.643
Thank you!

20:39.404 --> 20:40.405
Sorry about that.

20:52.918 --> 20:53.752
Hey.

20:56.463 --> 20:57.297
Yes?

20:58.090 --> 20:59.466
Are you feeling unwell?

21:02.511 --> 21:03.345
No.

21:04.012 --> 21:04.846
Okay.

21:05.597 --> 21:07.140
Let's focus on the lecture.

21:19.820 --> 21:22.114
Eun-ho, you're off to practice,
aren't you?

21:22.614 --> 21:23.782
I'm going to the library.

21:25.075 --> 21:27.077
Good. I was also on my way to the library.

21:27.160 --> 21:28.954
Come to think of it, I have practice.

21:30.831 --> 21:32.499
Me too. I have practice too.

21:59.985 --> 22:01.403
Should we get started first?

22:30.390 --> 22:31.308
What's he doing?

22:33.477 --> 22:34.436
Oh my God!

22:35.479 --> 22:36.563
Has he fallen for me?

22:54.122 --> 22:55.374
Don't you…

22:58.877 --> 23:00.295
go easy on me like last time.

23:05.050 --> 23:06.385
Give it everything you've got.

23:07.928 --> 23:08.762
This is bad.

23:11.973 --> 23:12.974
Put it on.

23:20.440 --> 23:22.984
I hurt his pride.

23:34.538 --> 23:36.039
Mi-rae, hi!

23:36.123 --> 23:37.666
Hello.

23:39.000 --> 23:40.001
What's going on?

23:40.669 --> 23:42.379
Did you two have a practice match?

23:43.672 --> 23:45.757
The thing is,

23:46.258 --> 23:47.175
Eun-ho…

23:47.259 --> 23:48.468
It was my idea.

23:53.306 --> 23:56.393
And? How did it go?

24:00.522 --> 24:02.023
MI-RAE, EUN-HO

24:02.107 --> 24:04.359
Wasn't I supposed to be a campus queen?

24:04.443 --> 24:06.611
They turned me into a full-on swordsman!

24:06.695 --> 24:08.280
WIN, LOSE

24:10.157 --> 24:11.366
No way.

24:11.867 --> 24:13.160
You lost?

24:16.163 --> 24:17.497
I don't believe it.

24:18.498 --> 24:19.332
Is it true?

24:22.711 --> 24:24.129
I'll go wash up.

24:36.266 --> 24:38.477
Let's go!

24:38.977 --> 24:41.354
Umchichi, umchichi, umchichi, umchichi!

24:41.438 --> 24:43.648
-Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny!
-Carrot, carrot!

24:44.232 --> 24:48.069
It's been so long since I've felt
this excitement, this youthful energy!

24:48.153 --> 24:49.154
Carrot, carrot!

24:49.237 --> 24:50.697
Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny!

24:50.780 --> 24:55.368
-Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny!
-Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny!

24:55.452 --> 24:57.954
You got it wrong, Jung-pil! Drink up!

24:58.538 --> 24:59.956
Drink up!

25:00.040 --> 25:01.041
I'd like to

25:02.209 --> 25:03.210
take one for him.

25:05.128 --> 25:07.714
-Hey! Give us a penalty drink!
-Penalty!

25:07.797 --> 25:08.798
Okay!

25:09.508 --> 25:10.675
Here comes the drink.

25:10.759 --> 25:11.635
Mi-rae!

25:11.718 --> 25:13.762
-Mi-rae!
-All right, mix it up.

25:16.389 --> 25:17.432
Get ready.

25:20.810 --> 25:21.978
Even soju?

25:28.193 --> 25:30.445
All right. Here's your penalty drink.

25:31.821 --> 25:33.615
Mi-rae, just

25:35.158 --> 25:37.202
what kind of life have you had?

25:37.285 --> 25:40.205
I got carried away.

25:40.288 --> 25:41.790
Is that how you do it?

25:42.332 --> 25:43.583
Eun-ho!

25:43.667 --> 25:44.960
-Hello, Eun-ho.
-Eun-ho!

25:45.043 --> 25:46.586
-Hi, Eun-ho.
-Come sit down.

25:47.796 --> 25:49.881
-Sit here.
-Hello, Eun-ho.

25:50.507 --> 25:52.008
Why are you so late?

25:52.092 --> 25:53.343
-Assignment.
-Have a drink.

25:53.426 --> 25:55.679
Bottoms up! Yeah!

25:57.097 --> 25:58.265
Su-ji, that's enough.

25:59.432 --> 26:02.143
No. I know you're a lightweight.

26:02.227 --> 26:03.228
Cheers.

26:03.311 --> 26:04.521
I'll drink it.

26:05.772 --> 26:09.234
I knew I didn't like that girl
from the start.

26:09.734 --> 26:11.903
She oddly reminds me of Na You-mi.

26:12.404 --> 26:13.697
You have something on you.

26:14.864 --> 26:15.740
Jung-pil!

26:16.491 --> 26:18.285
No, don't push yourself!

26:18.785 --> 26:20.704
You're going to feel sick tomorrow.

26:21.788 --> 26:24.708
By the way, Mi-rae,
have you done any sports before?

26:26.418 --> 26:27.502
Not at all.

26:28.628 --> 26:30.046
Oh, you're an art major.

26:30.130 --> 26:33.508
A talented artist and a skilled athlete.
You've got it all!

26:35.677 --> 26:38.430
Please! You flatter me.

26:41.099 --> 26:43.143
Too much humility can hurt you, you know.

26:44.561 --> 26:46.021
What are you talking about?

26:46.521 --> 26:48.148
Being humble is a good thing.

26:48.648 --> 26:50.275
Eun-ho's right about that one.

26:50.358 --> 26:53.945
It can get a bit annoying
when someone takes it too far.

26:54.029 --> 26:54.863
Yup.

26:56.239 --> 26:57.324
Excuse me.

26:57.949 --> 26:58.992
What?

26:59.075 --> 26:59.993
Not you.

27:03.496 --> 27:04.497
Do you hate me?

27:07.042 --> 27:07.876
What?

27:12.505 --> 27:14.049
I don't hate people.

27:15.717 --> 27:16.968
Sorry if you felt that way.

27:21.348 --> 27:22.474
That's a relief.

27:24.476 --> 27:26.144
-Mi-rae?
-Mi-rae.

27:26.227 --> 27:27.687
Where are you going?

27:34.402 --> 27:36.821
Because I like you, Eun-ho.

27:38.782 --> 27:40.825
-What?
-I think she's drunk!

27:40.909 --> 27:43.620
-Come on!
-Stop cutting in line, Mi-rae!

27:48.625 --> 27:50.460
You know, we've just met.

27:51.294 --> 27:52.128
What?

27:53.213 --> 27:54.923
You don't know me that well.

28:01.429 --> 28:04.015
Kids nowadays sure are bold,
don't you think?

28:04.099 --> 28:06.434
Jung-pil, you've got some pie on you.

28:06.518 --> 28:07.769
Man, that's embarrassing!

28:07.852 --> 28:08.853
Cutie-pie.

28:09.979 --> 28:11.106
-So cute.
-Is she mad?

28:11.189 --> 28:12.315
Hold on.

28:13.108 --> 28:13.942
-Cheers.
-Cheers.

28:14.025 --> 28:15.860
-Sounds good, Jung-pil!
-Here you go!

28:18.321 --> 28:19.406
What the heck?

28:19.489 --> 28:20.657
You're the best.

28:20.740 --> 28:22.200
-See you. Bye!
-Bye-bye!

28:22.283 --> 28:24.035
-You want to get in this one?
-May I?

28:24.119 --> 28:25.203
Yeah. Get in.

28:25.787 --> 28:27.122
Thank you.

28:27.205 --> 28:28.707
You should get in too.

28:49.310 --> 28:50.186
Where are you going?

28:51.062 --> 28:51.938
To campus.

28:53.356 --> 28:54.858
Oh, you live in the dorm.

28:56.359 --> 28:57.819
Are you going to campus too?

28:57.902 --> 29:00.363
Yes, to the library
to finish my assignment.

29:09.706 --> 29:11.666
You might as well just walk next to me.

29:11.750 --> 29:13.918
I don't want to feel
like I'm being chased.

29:21.926 --> 29:23.595
-Eun-ho.
-What?

29:25.013 --> 29:26.431
Do you like the club president?

29:27.474 --> 29:28.308
What?

29:31.019 --> 29:32.520
Maybe that was too direct.

29:33.730 --> 29:35.482
Fine. Where is your hometown?

29:35.565 --> 29:38.193
What's your type?
Are you into video games and stuff?

29:38.818 --> 29:39.694
What's up with you?

29:41.112 --> 29:44.741
You said I barely know you.
I want to get to know you quickly.

29:55.084 --> 29:55.919
Eun-ho!

29:59.672 --> 30:00.757
Run!

30:58.648 --> 31:00.942
You can't go to the library
all soaked like that.

31:01.025 --> 31:03.236
I have dry clothes in my bag.

31:03.945 --> 31:05.613
You should dry them off a bit.

31:10.660 --> 31:11.578
LAUNDRY ROOM

31:13.204 --> 31:14.747
Someone's doing their job!

31:15.790 --> 31:17.542
I'm sure they'll dry off in a bit.

31:18.585 --> 31:19.669
Take care.

31:19.752 --> 31:20.837
Wait!

31:23.172 --> 31:25.758
There's a way we can dry your clothes.

31:42.817 --> 31:44.319
Thanks for letting me in here.

31:45.737 --> 31:47.739
This takes a while, doesn't it?

31:48.781 --> 31:49.699
Yeah.

31:53.995 --> 31:55.496
You should go change too.

31:59.375 --> 32:00.460
Don't want to.

32:02.545 --> 32:05.048
I want to stay here with you, Eun-ho.

32:13.932 --> 32:15.183
You're one of a kind.

32:20.229 --> 32:21.814
You're really bold, aren't you?

32:34.744 --> 32:37.747
I didn't see this coming.

32:42.001 --> 32:42.961
Se-june.

32:43.920 --> 32:45.713
Here. Eat up.

32:48.341 --> 32:50.885
Mi-rae, why are you so bold?

32:51.719 --> 32:52.553
What did I do?

32:54.347 --> 32:55.556
Do you like me?

32:56.516 --> 32:57.350
Yes.

33:12.198 --> 33:13.408
Why is this jerk

33:14.200 --> 33:16.244
suddenly invading my thoughts?

33:58.453 --> 33:59.454
Eun-ho.

34:25.104 --> 34:26.856
You'll catch a cold.

34:28.066 --> 34:28.900
Dry your hair.

34:33.821 --> 34:35.406
And I don't like her.

34:40.995 --> 34:43.915
I'll be in the reading room
while the laundry finishes. See you.

34:44.999 --> 34:46.167
Wait…

34:46.751 --> 34:48.044
Don't catch a cold.

35:12.110 --> 35:14.737
What was that? So annoying.

35:26.999 --> 35:30.002
General You-mi only lets me post
flattering photos of her.

35:30.086 --> 35:31.796
I'll let it slide since she's cute.

35:31.879 --> 35:33.631
Hashtag, soon to be taken.

35:37.677 --> 35:39.554
What's this? You posted a photo?

35:42.890 --> 35:44.559
What? I don't like this photo.

35:45.309 --> 35:46.144
You don't?

35:46.727 --> 35:49.397
No. You should have asked me first.

35:50.648 --> 35:52.108
Only you look good.

35:52.191 --> 35:55.528
I posted it because you told me to.
What's wrong with you?

35:57.405 --> 35:59.073
Why are you snapping at me?

35:59.157 --> 36:02.326
I only said that because you didn't have
any photos of us dating.

36:03.953 --> 36:06.330
Okay. Sorry. You want it down, is that it?

36:07.874 --> 36:09.083
Never mind. Just leave it.

36:20.720 --> 36:22.722
BLOCK

36:47.496 --> 36:49.123
I'm doing fine too, you know.

36:52.627 --> 36:53.794
I'm happy too.

37:09.435 --> 37:13.731
Then again, there's no rule saying
I have to be doing fine in the real world.

37:49.892 --> 37:51.227
Let's go eat.

37:55.690 --> 37:56.941
Okay, Eun-ho!

37:57.775 --> 38:00.152
I heard the architecture program
is super hard.

38:00.236 --> 38:02.321
Jung-pil told me that, by the third year,

38:02.405 --> 38:04.991
your blood is basically coffee
from all the all-nighters.

38:06.117 --> 38:09.161
But I don't think
I've ever seen you drink coffee.

38:09.245 --> 38:10.288
Don't you like coffee?

38:10.371 --> 38:12.665
Oh, I'm guessing
caffeine doesn't agree with you.

38:13.416 --> 38:15.251
Want to go to a café after this?

38:17.128 --> 38:19.255
Love it. I like lattes.

38:19.338 --> 38:20.589
You like lattes?

38:41.319 --> 38:42.570
All done.

38:43.237 --> 38:44.071
What do you think?

38:44.655 --> 38:45.656
You nailed it.

39:07.386 --> 39:10.598
Like trying to paint over
old memories with new ones…

39:19.190 --> 39:21.442
I immersed myself in Boyfriend on Demand.

39:28.282 --> 39:29.408
Eun-ho.

39:33.245 --> 39:34.413
How did it go?

39:35.289 --> 39:36.290
The exam?

39:36.374 --> 39:37.792
I blew it.

39:43.005 --> 39:43.923
Because of you.

39:56.852 --> 40:00.648
Is it true that a kumdo practitioner
could beat anyone with just chopsticks?

40:01.273 --> 40:03.067
-Drinking game?
-Let's go!

40:04.276 --> 40:05.152
Bunny bunny?

40:05.653 --> 40:07.530
Not even. Don't be ridiculous.

40:08.155 --> 40:10.366
Why not? You can stab people with them.

40:10.449 --> 40:13.285
-Aim for the vital spots.
-Bunny, bunny! Carrot, carrot!

40:13.369 --> 40:14.203
Stab!

40:14.286 --> 40:15.871
Carrot, carrot!

40:16.539 --> 40:18.791
No thrusts allowed until you're third dan.

40:18.874 --> 40:19.917
Why?

40:22.336 --> 40:24.380
Why are you outside by yourself?

40:27.675 --> 40:29.176
Can I ask you something?

40:31.303 --> 40:32.138
Sure.

40:33.848 --> 40:35.307
To you, am I still…

40:38.978 --> 40:40.312
just an upperclassman?

40:47.236 --> 40:48.654
Why did I quit being an author?

40:48.737 --> 40:50.823
Kim Baek-chun, the author, said to me,

40:50.906 --> 40:53.159
"Hey, kid, you should give up
on being an author."

40:53.242 --> 40:57.037
That's why I quit.
That's how tight we are.

40:57.121 --> 40:58.247
What's wrong with you?

40:58.330 --> 40:59.832
Wow, you're indebted to him.

41:00.916 --> 41:03.419
-What was that?
-You're indebted to him. Indebted.

41:07.131 --> 41:09.884
What? There wasn't any rain
in the forecast.

41:22.438 --> 41:24.773
You came to a company dinner.
How unlike you.

41:25.274 --> 41:28.360
Yeah, it felt kind of awkward
to go home for dinner.

41:29.028 --> 41:29.862
I see.

41:31.906 --> 41:32.990
Are you heading home?

41:33.073 --> 41:34.200
Yes, I am

41:35.326 --> 41:36.327
not.

41:37.161 --> 41:38.204
You're not going home?

41:39.288 --> 41:41.499
-Then back to the office?
-Seriously?

41:41.999 --> 41:44.001
Does he think I have nowhere else to be?

41:44.084 --> 41:46.837
Oh, well, I have a date, you see.

41:49.673 --> 41:50.508
I see.

42:00.643 --> 42:01.769
He'll be picking you up?

42:02.770 --> 42:03.604
Yes.

42:04.730 --> 42:05.898
Enjoy your date, then.

42:13.030 --> 42:15.241
A date, really? Have you lost it?

42:35.886 --> 42:36.887
I'm freezing.

42:55.990 --> 42:57.533
VISUAL DESIGN CLASS GROUP CHAT
NA YOU-MI

42:57.616 --> 43:00.160
Here is our mobile wedding invitation.

43:00.244 --> 43:02.830
You are cordially invited
to Se-june and You-mi's wedding!

43:02.913 --> 43:04.957
MOBILE WEDDING INVITATION

43:05.916 --> 43:08.586
SUNDAY, NOVEMBER 23, 2025
KIM SE-JUNE, NA YOU-MI

43:13.757 --> 43:18.053
Oh my God, you two look great together!
Congratulations, You-mi and Se-june.

43:18.137 --> 43:20.598
You-mi, you look so pretty.

43:20.681 --> 43:22.933
You'd better treat her well, Se-june.

43:23.225 --> 43:24.059
JI-YEON

43:24.143 --> 43:27.479
Is she out of her mind?
She totally knew you were in this chat.

43:53.005 --> 43:54.048
Hello.

43:55.507 --> 43:57.343
It's me. Did you have my number?

43:59.595 --> 44:00.512
No.

44:02.765 --> 44:04.433
At least you recognized my voice.

44:05.517 --> 44:06.435
Why did you call?

44:08.228 --> 44:11.273
Well, it's just, You-mi…

44:12.900 --> 44:15.736
Damn, the thing she posted on the chat
is bothering me.

44:16.487 --> 44:17.446
Did you see it?

44:20.074 --> 44:20.908
Yeah.

44:21.909 --> 44:23.118
You guys look happy.

44:24.161 --> 44:25.120
I'm sorry.

44:29.208 --> 44:30.209
About what?

44:31.502 --> 44:32.920
For making you see that.

44:34.588 --> 44:35.422
It…

44:36.757 --> 44:39.426
It wasn't so different
from any other invitation.

44:44.765 --> 44:47.267
Right. I'm glad you're okay with it.

44:48.394 --> 44:49.269
Yeah.

44:54.400 --> 44:56.485
I'm hanging up now. Take care.

45:01.657 --> 45:02.616
Yeah.

45:29.309 --> 45:31.145
NOTIFICATION

45:35.190 --> 45:40.487
Ms. Seo Mi-rae, four hours remain
until your subscription expires.

45:42.823 --> 45:44.158
Today, of all days?

46:01.383 --> 46:04.970
I'm so sorry, but I love you
It's all a lie

46:05.053 --> 46:09.808
I had no idea, I finally get it
I need you

46:09.892 --> 46:12.895
Sorry, but I love you
Those piercing words

46:12.978 --> 46:17.107
In the heat of the moment
I ended up letting you go

46:17.191 --> 46:20.277
I'm so sorry, but I love you
It's all a lie

46:20.360 --> 46:21.361
Together now!

46:27.868 --> 46:30.120
Mi-rae.

46:32.206 --> 46:33.749
You can't just walk away like that.

46:34.416 --> 46:36.960
I did because you were talking nonsense.

46:37.044 --> 46:38.670
-Let go.
-I can't.

46:38.754 --> 46:40.798
If I let go, you'll just leave,

46:41.423 --> 46:44.927
and you'll blame yourself
for letting our last moment end like this.

46:45.010 --> 46:47.346
I'll deal with it myself. Let me go.

46:48.222 --> 46:49.515
I said let go!

46:52.226 --> 46:53.060
Why?

46:53.977 --> 46:56.355
You broke up with me.
Why won't you let me leave?

46:57.439 --> 46:58.649
Who do you think you are?

46:59.441 --> 47:01.109
Just who do you think you are?

47:12.871 --> 47:16.834
I may have brought it up first,
but we both already knew

47:17.960 --> 47:19.336
that things had changed.

47:21.338 --> 47:22.923
That's what you think.

47:23.674 --> 47:24.967
I never changed.

47:26.176 --> 47:27.010
Mi-rae.

47:29.304 --> 47:30.806
We all change.

47:33.225 --> 47:34.643
You've also changed.

47:36.603 --> 47:38.438
If I can love you

47:39.356 --> 47:41.525
for who you've become,

47:42.568 --> 47:44.695
that would mean
we can be together forever.

47:46.655 --> 47:47.781
But I…

47:50.534 --> 47:52.911
I'm not sure if I can do that with you.

48:51.136 --> 48:53.263
-Wow, look.
-It's beautiful.

48:53.347 --> 48:54.681
-What is this place?
-Amazing.

49:01.063 --> 49:03.023
-Let's take pictures.
-It's lovely.

49:08.904 --> 49:10.072
Is something wrong?

49:24.461 --> 49:26.421
I don't know what's going on,

49:27.923 --> 49:31.301
but get some sleep
and just clear your mind.

50:05.502 --> 50:06.712
You know what?

50:07.337 --> 50:08.505
Ever since we broke up,

50:09.089 --> 50:13.260
I've never once thought back
to our early days together.

50:50.422 --> 50:52.299
-Cheers!
-Finish it off!

51:09.983 --> 51:11.610
Se-june!

51:28.001 --> 51:29.419
SEO MI-RAE

51:31.546 --> 51:32.631
Don't I look good?

51:34.091 --> 51:35.592
For your first day at work.

51:37.094 --> 51:37.928
Thanks!

51:59.533 --> 52:00.450
Got some sleep?

52:01.368 --> 52:02.953
You had a long day.

52:06.081 --> 52:08.959
Because you had changed anyway.

52:09.459 --> 52:11.294
Because we were over anyway.

52:12.337 --> 52:15.006
Because I hated your guts so much.

52:18.385 --> 52:19.469
But

52:20.303 --> 52:23.640
being in here brought the memories back,
and strangely…

52:29.563 --> 52:30.814
I don't hate you now.

52:37.696 --> 52:43.994
HANSAE KUMDO CLUB
FRESHMAN WELCOME TRIP

52:51.710 --> 52:53.503
We're here. Let's get off.

53:09.936 --> 53:10.770
Over there.

53:12.355 --> 53:13.648
It's a shooting star.

53:16.985 --> 53:18.111
Want to see it up close?

53:22.699 --> 53:24.117
Is there something here?

53:24.618 --> 53:25.785
You'll see.

54:04.532 --> 54:05.450
Eun-ho.

54:09.204 --> 54:10.705
Do you like me now?

54:15.877 --> 54:17.087
Still not there yet?

54:35.146 --> 54:36.481
Eun-ho.

54:38.900 --> 54:41.361
If you end up marrying
someone other than me,

54:42.195 --> 54:43.863
will you forget about me?

54:45.240 --> 54:46.449
What do you mean?

54:52.497 --> 54:55.500
It's not like you lose your memories
when you marry someone.

54:55.583 --> 54:57.294
I'm sure I'll remember everything.

54:59.170 --> 55:00.588
My heart may forget…

55:02.590 --> 55:04.175
but the memories will remain.

55:08.013 --> 55:09.931
How will you remember me?

55:14.602 --> 55:16.062
The way I was in the end?

55:17.772 --> 55:18.773
Or

55:20.275 --> 55:21.568
in the beginning?

55:22.819 --> 55:24.237
It's all you.

55:27.490 --> 55:28.825
I'll remember it all.

55:30.910 --> 55:31.786
The beginning…

55:33.872 --> 55:34.789
and the end.

55:43.423 --> 55:44.341
Okay.

55:45.842 --> 55:47.260
That will do.

56:17.957 --> 56:19.125
Have a good life.

56:22.379 --> 56:23.254
You too.

56:45.443 --> 56:47.529
You sound like you're about to go away.

56:54.911 --> 56:55.912
You must be cold.

01:00:38.718 --> 01:00:43.723
Subtitle translation by: Daham Yoon
